{"_path":"/post/20260703-sqlite-turso-single-writer-wal-batch","_dir":"post","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"前端工程師的 SQLite 震撼教育：全庫寫鎖、WAL、還有 batch 為什麼差四百倍","description":"我是前端工程師，對資料庫的心智模型來自 MySQL/Postgres 的常識：row-level lock、多個連線併發寫入、connection pool。直到我用 Turso（雲端版 SQLite / libSQL）跑了一個爬蟲系統、經歷了幾次事故（覆盤見系列上一篇），才發現這套常識在 SQLite 世界整組不適用。","tags":"sqlite, turso, libsql, database, hrana, 資料庫, 後端開發, 技術筆記","createdByAI":true,"customCreatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:03:00.000Z","readingTime":{"text":"9 min read","minutes":8.2,"time":492000,"words":1640},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我是前端工程師，對資料庫的心智模型來自 MySQL/Postgres 的常識：row-level lock、多個連線併發寫入、connection pool。直到我用 Turso（雲端版 SQLite / libSQL）跑了一個爬蟲系統、經歷了幾次事故（覆盤見系列上一篇），才發現這套常識在 SQLite 世界"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"整組不適用"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這篇整理我補課學到的 SQLite 併發模型——如果你也是從 row-lock 資料庫的直覺出發來用 SQLite / Turso / Cloudflare D1，這些反直覺的點大概也會咬到你。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"不是鎖表是鎖整個資料庫"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不是鎖表，是鎖整個資料庫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我原本以為 SQLite 寫入時「會鎖整張表」，已經覺得夠粗了。實情更粗一級："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"整個資料庫同一時間只允許一個寫入者"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，鎖的粒度是整個資料庫"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為什麼？因為鎖的粒度跟著儲存單位走。MySQL/Postgres 是一個 server 程序管理表空間、分頁、資料列，所以鎖可以做細；SQLite 的設計是「一個檔案就是一個資料庫」，鎖本質上就是檔案層級的鎖。不是它偷懶，是儲存模型決定的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三個直接推論："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多連線不會加速寫入。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" N 個連線同時寫，到了資料庫端全部排隊串行化。我的爬蟲曾經開 10 條平行連線各自寫入，平行的其實只有上游 API 的抓取——DB 寫入端永遠是單線道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"connection pool 是 row-lock 資料庫的習俗"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，搬過來只是多付連線成本。單例 client 就是正確設計。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transaction 開多久，全世界的寫入就排隊多久。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 這讓「transaction 裡夾網路呼叫」從壞習慣升級成災難——你拿著全庫唯一的寫鎖去等一個外部 API。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"wal讀不被寫擋但它不是讀寫分離"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"WAL：讀不被寫擋，但它不是讀寫分離"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"聽到「寫入時鎖整庫」，直覺的下一個恐慌是：那讀取不就也被擋住？不會——現代 SQLite（包含 Turso）跑 WAL（Write-Ahead Logging）模式：寫入者把新資料 append 到 WAL 檔尾巴，讀取者沿用自己開始那一刻的快照視圖，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讀不擋寫、寫不擋讀"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-1-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我第一反應是「這不就是讀寫分離？」——像，但層次完全不同，值得校準："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讀寫分離（read replica）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"WAL 模式"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本質"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"拓撲"}]},{"type":"text","value":"模式：兩台以上機器"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單機儲存引擎"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的日誌技巧"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一致性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"replica 有複製延遲，讀到舊資料是常態"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"commit 後的下一個讀取立刻看到新資料，強一致"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目的"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水平擴展讀取容量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單機上的讀寫併發"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"機制上更準的類比是 Postgres 的 MVCC 快照隔離——「讀舊版本、寫新版本、互不相擾」是同一族的思想。有趣的是，Turso 的 edge replica 功能才是真的讀寫分離，而它的實作恰好就是把 WAL frames 運送到各地。WAL 是磚，讀寫分離是可以用這種磚蓋出來的房子之一。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"batch-為什麼差四百倍你付的是每筆交易的固定成本"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"batch 為什麼差四百倍：你付的是每筆交易的固定成本"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這是最有感的一課。同樣寫入 3.8 萬筆資料到 Turso："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"估算耗時"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為什麼"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"逐筆 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"execute()"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"~95 分鐘"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每筆一次 HTTPS 往返（~150ms）× 38,000"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單一 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"batch()"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"~13 秒"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全部 statements 打包成一個請求"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫入的成本分三層，batch 的意義是把「每筆付一次」變成「整包付一次」："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Commit 成本（SQLite 本體）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每次 commit 是一次 fsync（磁碟寫入屏障）。SQLite 官方 FAQ 的名句：它每秒能執行 50,000 條 INSERT，但每秒只能完成幾十個 transaction"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-2","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"——"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"慢的從來不是 INSERT，是 commit"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。autocommit 模式（不包 transaction）等於每條 statement 自帶一次 commit。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網路往返（遠端 DB 加成）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Turso 的每個請求是一次 HTTPS round trip，跨區域 ~100-200ms，比 fsync 貴兩個數量級。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鎖排程"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每個 transaction 拿放一次全庫寫鎖。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"batch 也有代價：整包是單一 transaction、全有全無（通常是優點，但失敗就整包重來）；單次鎖持有時間變長；payload 變大。所以不是越大越好，一般甜蜜點在每批 500–2000 筆。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"hrana為-fetch-時代重造的資料庫協議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hrana：為 fetch() 時代重造的資料庫協議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最後補一塊讓我「一片陌生就在用」的拼圖：client 和 Turso 之間在網路上說的話，是一個叫 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hrana"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的協議"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-3","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-3"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"（捷克文「邊緣」）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它存在的理由：傳統資料庫的線路協議是有狀態的二進位 TCP 長連線，在 serverless/edge 環境（沒有 raw socket、冷啟動頻繁）根本養不起。hrana 的答案是把資料庫協議建立在 HTTP/WebSocket 之上——"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任何有 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"fetch()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的地方就能當資料庫 client"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。一個 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"execute"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 就是一個 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"POST /v2/pipeline"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、body 是 JSON。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兩個核心概念："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pipeline"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：把多個操作打包成一個 HTTP POST。前面說的「batch 只付一次往返」，機制就是它。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Baton"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：跨請求的會話接力棒，像 DB 版的 session cookie"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-3","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-3-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。HTTP 無狀態，那開到一半的 transaction 怎麼跨請求存活？server 每次回應帶一個 baton，client 下次請求帶上。這也精確解釋了「互動式 transaction 走 HTTP 為什麼危險」——"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全庫寫鎖在兩次往返之間掛在 server 上等你"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"順帶一提：正因為協議是 fetch 原生的，你可以對 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"createClient"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 注入自訂 fetch，在請求層做 timeout、abort、觀測——這在傳統二進位協議的資料庫上無從下手。我們就是靠這一點修掉了連線 black-hole 的事故（見系列上一篇）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"五條實用法則"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"五條實用法則"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transaction 裡絕對不要夾網路呼叫"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——先在記憶體組好完整的 statements 陣列，一次 "},{"type":"element